```dockerfile
FROM maven:3.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build
COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve
COPY . .
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="analytics@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Java Analytics Dashboard"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apk add --no-cache \
    curl \
    fontconfig \
    ttf-dejavu \
    ca-certificates && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

RUN mkdir -p /tmp/certs && cd /tmp/certs && \
    curl -sS https://truststore.pem.s3.amazonaws.com/rds-ca-2019-root.pem -o rds-ca-2019-root.pem && \
    curl -sS https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt.pem -o DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca-2019-root -file rds-ca-2019-root.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    keytool -import -alias digicert-global-root -file DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt || true && \
    rm -rf /tmp/certs

RUN addgroup -S appgroup && adduser -S -u 1001 -G appgroup app

COPY --from=builder /build/target/app.jar /app/app.jar

RUN chown -R app:appgroup /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
